7-1.562-1.562-4.095-1.563-5.657 0l-3.841 3.841-.333-.009c-.404 0-.802.04-1.189.117l4.656-4.656c.975-.976 2.256-1.464 3.536-1.464 1.279 0 2.56.488 3.535 1.464 1.951 1.951 1.951 5.119 0 7.071l-4.999 4.998c-.975.976-2.255 1.464-3.535 1.464-1.28 0-2.56-.488-3.535-1.464-.494-.495-.863-1.067-1.107-1.678l.788-.785z\"/></svg></a>ReactJS + NextJS</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://nextjs.org/\">https://nextjs.org/</a></p>\n<p>Next JS for the frontend to make a quality single-page-application (SPA).</p>\n<h2 id=\"references-and-further-reading\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#references-and-further-reading\" aria-label=\"references and further reading permalink\" class=\"custom-class before\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"><path d=\"M14.851 11.923c-.179-.641-.521-1.246-1.025-1.749-1.562-1.562-4.095-1.563-5.657 0l-4.998 4.998c-1.562 1.563-1.563 4.095 0 5.657 1.562 1.563 4.096 1.561 5.656 0l3.842-3.841.333.009c.404 0 .802-.04 1.189-.117l-4.657 4.656c-.975.976-2.255 1.464-3.535 1.464-1.28 0-2.56-.488-3.535-1.464-1.952-1.951-1.952-5.12 0-7.071l4.998-4.998c.975-.976 2.256-1.464 3.536-1.464 1.279 0 2.56.488 3.535 1.464.493.493.861 1.063 1.105 1.672l-.787.784zm-5.703.147c.178.643.521 1.25 1.026 1.756 1.562 1.563 4.096 1.561 5.656 0l4.999-4.998c1.563-1.562 1.563-4.095 0-5.657-1.562-1.562-4.095-1.563-5.657 0l-3.841 3.841-.333-.009c-.404 0-.802.04-1.189.117l4.656-4.656c.975-.976 2.256-1.464 3.536-1.464 1.279 0 2.56.488 3.535 1.464 1.951 1.951 1.951 5.119 0 7.071l-4.999 4.998c-.975.976-2.255 1.464-3.535 1.464-1.28 0-2.56-.488-3.535-1.464-.494-.495-.863-1.067-1.107-1.678l.788-.785z\"/></svg></a>References and Further Reading</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Course: Foundations of Local Large Language models by Duke University <a href=\"https://www.coursera.org/learn/local-large-language-models/\">https://www.coursera.org/learn/local-large-language-models/</a></li>\n<li>Ollama <a href=\"https://github.